#CHIP SegaPCM
#CLOCK 7670454

; SegaPCM (Sega Genesis) Basic Test — 16-channel sample playback
;
; The Sega Genesis/Mega Drive includes a built-in PCM sample player
; capable of playing up to 16 simultaneous samples with:
; - Individual pitch control
; - Volume/envelope control
; - Loop points
;
; Tests:
; - All 16 channels
; - Pitch modulation
; - Volume envelope

#TRACK 0

TEMPO 120

; Channels 1-4: Melodic sequence
c4 . d4 . e4 . f4 .

r4

; Channels 5-8: Offset by octave
c3 . d3 . e3 . f3 .

r4

; Channels 9-12: Harmony
g4 . a4 . b4 . >c5 .

r4

; Channels 13-16: Bass foundation
c2 . . c2 . . c2 . .

r4

r2

#END
